			<p>Users are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of their account information and for all activities under their account.</p>

			<h2>4. Intellectual Property</h2>
			<p>All content and materials available on Glow Trading are protected by applicable intellectual property laws.</p>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	main {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 2rem;
	}

	h1 {
		font-size: 3rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		color: var(--color-primary);
	}

	.last-updated {
		color: #666;
		font-style: italic;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	h2 {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
		color: var(--color-accent);
	}

	.content {
		line-height: 1.6;
	}
</style> 